@RanaAyyub Dear, the industrialists are already taxed multiple times - GST, corporate taxes, Income tax, etc 

Only ~ 5 % population pays income tax

Why don’t you ask to tax rich farmers like Cauliflower farmer &amp; Vangi tai?

@RanaAyyub Do you want the Indian government to tax the Rich &amp; fund the 🐷s?
No.....
India is not breeding ground for 🐷s

@RanaAyyub Are kana ji 2014 tak ye 70% own karte they ab 40% me aa gaye hn.... Itna badlaw na dikh rha ke...??

Or baat rahi taxation ki to inhi ke 40%tax se tumhari karwi jiwha ko chalane ka mouka provide karwati h ye govt.

Wrna 40-40 suanr paida karne wale abhi tak Afghanistan bana dete.

